{% if config.architecture.framework_name %}
### A1. Layer Declaration and Boundaries

Reference: `{{ config.paths.architecture_doc | default('docs/ai/system_architecture.md') }}` (baseline). **Read this document before completing this section.**

| Check | Status | Notes |
|-------|--------|-------|
| Plan declares Architecture Layer(s) in metadata? | [ ] | Layer(s): |
| Plan consumes output from the upstream layer (does NOT bypass)? | [ ] | |
| Plan output format matches expected layer output? | [ ] | |
| Plan is consistent with current architecture document version? | [ ] | Version checked: |
| If plan proposes architectural changes: amendment added to changelog? | [ ] | N/A if no changes |
| Plan creates files in locations matching architecture document? | [ ] | |
| Module boundaries respected (no cross-layer imports)? | [ ] | |
| Naming conventions match existing codebase? | [ ] | |
| No duplicate functionality with existing/planned modules? | [ ] | |

### A2. Data Flow Traceability

For each data input the plan consumes, trace it back to its origin layer.
Flag any input that skips an intermediate layer.

| Data Input | Source Layer | Expected Path | Bypasses Layer? | Notes |
|------------|-------------|---------------|-----------------|-------|
| | | | [ ] Yes / No | |

**If any "Yes" in Bypasses Layer:** document why the bypass exists and whether
it can be corrected. If the bypass cannot be justified, update the plan before proceeding.

### A3. Service Connection Audit

For each new import, API call, or message flow the plan introduces, verify it
connects to the correct architectural layer.

| Connection | From (Layer) | To (Layer) | Follows layer boundaries? | Notes |
|------------|-------------|------------|---------------------------|-------|
| | | | [ ] Yes / No | |

{% if config.architecture.anti_patterns %}**Layer-bypass anti-patterns to check for:**
{% for pattern in config.architecture.anti_patterns %}- [ ] {{ pattern }}
{% endfor %}{% endif %}

### A4. Alignment Decision

| Decision | Status |
|----------|--------|
| All data flows respect layer boundaries | [ ] Pass / [ ] Fail |
| All service connections follow architecture | [ ] Pass / [ ] Fail |
| **Overall: proceed with implementation?** | [ ] Yes / [ ] No -- fix plan first |

If "No": document required corrections and update plan before proceeding.
